succeed a Wisdom saving throw (DC 14) or be frightened by a creature of the DMâs choosing for the next minute. (14)","img":"https://static.thenounproject.com/png/1972518-200.png","resultId":null,"weight":1,"range":[14,14],"drawn":false,"collection":null,"rangeL":14,"rangeH":14},{"_id":"ZGViZTA3YTVmYjlh","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Mute. Whenever you wish to speak allowed (including casting a spell that has verbal components) you must succeed on a Wisdom saving throw (DC 13) to do so. (15)","img":"https://static.thenounproject.com/png/1130062-200.png","resultId":null,"weight":1,"range":[15,15],"drawn":false,"collection":null,"rangeL":15,"rangeH":15},{"_id":"NDI5NTYzMTY2N2Iw","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Narcolepsy. You have disadvantage on saving throws against sleeping or unconsciousness. Once per day the DM may call on you to succeed on a Constitution saving throw (DC 12) or fall unconscious for one minute or until you take damage or another creature spends their action trying to rouse you. (16)","img":"https://static.thenounproject.com/png/2686184-200.png","resultId":null,"weight":1,"range":[16,16],"drawn":false,"collection":null,"rangeL":16,"rangeH":16},{"_id":"OTQ0NGEyMDAzOGNj","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Insomnia. You cannot take long rests and your short rests take 8 hours to complete. (17)","img":"https://static.thenounproject.com/png/2411492-200.png","resultId":null,"weight":1,"range":[17,17],"drawn":false,"collection":null,"rangeL":17,"rangeH":17},{"_id":"ZGFlNmFkZTA1YWQ3","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Homicidal. After each long rest you must pass a Wisdom saving throw (DC 14) or be overcome with the urge to end the life of a humanoid creature and you cannot benefit from another long rest until you do so. (18)","img":"https://static.thenounproject.com/png/15069-200.png","resultId":null,"weight":1,"range":[18,18],"drawn":false,"collection":null,"rangeL":18,"rangeH":18},{"_id":"ZDQ0MTJjOGZkYjlh","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Suicidal. After each long rest you must pass a Wisdom saving throw (DC 12) or make an attempt to end your own life. (19)","img":"https://static.thenounproject.com/png/3074832-200.png","resultId":null,"weight":1,"range":[19,19],"drawn":false,"collection":null,"rangeL":19,"rangeH":19},{"_id":"OGU3OGVjZmVkN2Ew","flags":{},"type":0,"text":"Catatonia. You are unconscious for 10d10 years. (20)","img":"https://static.thenounproject.com/png/2047507-200.png","resultId":null,"weight":1,"range":[20,20],"drawn":false,"collection":null,"rangeL":20,"rangeH":20}],"formula":"1d20","replacement":true,"displayRoll":true,"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"chBZeKgbHJ17qeha":3},"flags":{"exportSource":{"world":"avernum-thepit","system":"dnd5e","coreVersion":"0.7.5","systemVersion":0.96}}}
